  "body": "### Description\n\nWhen working on a Quarkus-based CLI app (using Picocli), I can easily re-run the very last command in dev mode. Oftentimes I'm alternating between multiple commands though, which currently means that I need to re-enter the command each time it changes (typically by copy & pasting from some text file).\r\n\r\nSuggestion: provide a history of commands executed in dev mode and let me easily re-execute earlier commands, e.g. by going through the history with Ctrl+R, or by simply typing 1, 2, 3, etc. for selecting earlier commands.\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
